data.description:
Looking for a place to stretch out? You will find plenty of room in this 5 bedroom 2 bath home situated just off Pineville road in Pass Christian. The carpeted, freshly steam cleaned den is so spacious that the entire family can relax and spend time together in one room while not feeling constricted. The kitchen boasts a large walk-in pantry, beautiful granite countertops and the cutest little breakfast bar that leads you to a large formal dining room with additional sitting area & study nook. As you stroll down the hall you will find FIVE bedrooms, two full baths, and a nicely spacious laundry room. Come home to Turan Street in Pass Christian. You won't want to live anywhere else.
Note: Sellers began removing flooring in kitchen, sub floor exposed. Some soft spots in kitchen and entryway by door. Attic was just re-insulated, most walls have been re-painted, and carpets have been professionally steam cleaned.
Two out buildings on the property, one large enough to be used as a workshop, craft area, etc. Covered lean-to for safely storing lawn mower, yard equipment & tools. May qualify for 203k Renovation loan
All offers must include verification of funds letter or lender pre-approval. Closing at Pilger Title in Long Beach
